<li>Run and add this URL to Eclipse's list of available update sites:<!--[CodeBlockStart:638dbe3c-3c4c-4d1c-9798-4ef3732b30a4]--><pre class="jive-pre"><code class="jive-code"><a class="jive-link-external-small" href="http://download.jboss.org/jbosstools/updates/development/indigo" target="_blank">http://download.jboss.org/jbosstools/updates/development/indigo</a></code></pre>
